{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"1370","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":null,"news_on_top":"1","news_title":"世界經濟論壇：能源糧食飆漲恐持續至2025年","news_summary":null,"image_path":null,"news_des":"","news_content":"<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>2023-01-11 22:57 聯合報／編譯陳韋廷／即時報導</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90%E7%B3%A7%E9%A3%9F.jpg' style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; width: 100%;' /></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>世界經濟論壇11日發布報告示警稱全球生活成本危機恐持續到2025年。法新社</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<hr style='box-sizing: content-box; border-radius: 0px; height: 1px; margin: 20px 0px; border-top-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); background-image: -webkit-linear-gradient(left, transparent, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), transparent); color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;' />\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>世界經濟論壇（WEF）11日發布年度全球風險報告示警，未來兩年能源與糧食價格飆漲的情形恐將持續，成為全球經濟面臨的最大風險，其次則是自然災害、極端天氣事件和地緣經濟對抗。</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>WEF在報告中指出，新冠疫情與俄烏戰爭引發了一系列相互關聯的全球風險，後果恐破壞各國在應對氣候危機、保護生物多樣性和減少貧困等長期問題上的合作。</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>該報告由諮詢服務業者Marsh McLennan與蘇黎世保險集團共同完成，研究報告還納入了1200多名全球風險專家、政策制定者和產業領袖的觀點。</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>世界經濟論壇年會將於16日在瑞士度假小鎮達沃斯開幕，今年主題為「破碎世界中的合作」（cooperation in a fragmented world）。</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'>資料來源:&nbsp;</span><a href='https://udn.com/news/story/6809/6904303' style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 158, 184); text-decoration-line: none; outline: 0px !important;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>https://udn.com/news/story/6809/6904303</span></a></span></p>\r\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2023-01-16","clk_count":"55"}},"__N_SSG":true}